    {
      "id": "Route203_Text_YourFavoritePokemonShouldBePlacedAtTheTop",
      "en_US": [
        "Your favorite Pokémon should be placed\n",
        "at the top left of your party list.\r",
        "That way, it will be the first to go out\n",
        "in a battle."
      ]
    },
    {
